{"tid":1072463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國盃】國足0：1負泰國無緣決賽　 簡拿華路首度領軍敗陣　「泰國美斯」奠勝 (22:25)","createTime":"2019-03-22T04:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T05:09:36.000Z","uid":5649,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9790cc32735adfb13128a4aea267d23cf24a17ef","tid":1072463,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190321/s00006/45f4ebd9c3e4664d4446d1527606d75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190321%2Fs00006%2F45f4ebd9c3e4664d4446d1527606d75b.jpg&h=674fadb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國隊（國足）兼職新帥簡拿華路今晚首度領軍「落筆打三更」，在中國盃面對亞洲盃手下敗將泰國隊，最終被「泰國美斯」猜拿迪普桑格辛一箭定江山，主場以0：1敗陣，連續3屆無緣決賽。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n國足自名帥納比在亞洲盃後離任，由師承他的簡拿華路兼任。銳意年輕化的國足，今次未有徵召老將鄭智及效力西甲愛斯賓奴的前鋒武磊，執教中超廣州恒大的「大簡」，亦帶同了8名恒大球員入隊。兩個月前的亞洲盃16強，中國以2：1反勝泰國晉級，今次兩軍再戰，國足有首獲徵召的上海上港前鋒呂文君正選，亦有兩名年輕球員高準翼及韋世豪「擔正」。泰國則有隊長鄧達等人因傷退隊，由日職北海道札幌岡薩多主力、有「泰國美斯」之稱的猜拿迪普桑格辛領軍。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190321/s00006/45f4a5a7ee9cd3386330fa2097b262c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190321%2Fs00006%2F45f4a5a7ee9cd3386330fa2097b262c3.jpg&h=fe903999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n今仗在廣西南寧開賽，東道主國足在上半場卻受壓，被客軍的猜拿迪連番進襲，結果在33分鐘，便被身高僅1.58米的「泰國美斯」，殺入禁區接應地波傳中熨射得手，為泰國領先1：0，完半場前，韋世豪有兩次射門機會均被門將施華拉撲出後，國足半場落後1球。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190321/s00006/45f486f5ef58384c3f024aeae267e606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190321%2Fs00006%2F45f486f5ef58384c3f024aeae267e606.jpg&h=042f09aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n換邊後，國足有多次攻門機會，中場蒿俊閔起腳射高，前鋒董學升亦頭槌攻門頂高，反觀泰國前鋒艾迪薩有次擴大比數良機，在禁區無人看管下起腳，但被今仗連番撲救的國足門將顏駿凌再一次飛身撲出。及後國足傾力反撲無功而還下，最終以0：1落敗。泰國晉身下周一決賽，將與明晚出場的烏茲別克或烏拉圭爭標。<br />\n<br />\n入波條友叫猜拿，中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3374f97bf67d8c069d7053b82df1a2fe9c8e3a31","tid":1072463,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"無磊無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de76f8afffe82660e1e4eb3cedab1381d52624f3","tid":1072463,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"大簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc2068cd3e1a4ddfaf298e8c7c06b49ac2cb26e","tid":1072463,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"中華秦國"},{"pid":"10f9f73f4a7af5044a09ad4b420d3c1b2f3d361c","tid":1072463,"uid":30370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"下次請聖馬力諾算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4498e8fa8acee99257ea87790878d22be12ae56c","tid":1072463,"uid":60281,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJ8ucOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJ8ucOc.png&h=6f664823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0905025277f743b0b897704ba244a75193848d81","tid":1072463,"uid":153154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4498e8fa8acee99257ea87790878d22be12ae56c","tid":1072463,"uid":60281,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJ8ucOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJ8ucOc.png&h=6f664823&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸就當係集訓隊<br />\n下世都